{"TopicId":209512,"ForumId":112,"TopicTitle":"can we have steam achievements?","CreatedByName":"hooray","CreatedById":222633,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-26T02:53:45Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"hooray","CreatedById":222633,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-26T02:53:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nATT and some\u00A0points shop things..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-26T09:53:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a possibility, why not\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-26T10:24:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA couple suggestions:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EA special kind of talent\u003C/strong\u003E - Destroy 2 or more \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E buildings in a single crash.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDid you check the map?\u003C/strong\u003E - Leave Kerbin\u0027s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E without having entered Mun\u0027s or Minmus\u0027 SOIs\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"intelliCom","CreatedById":209738,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-26T14:14:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224167481\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209512\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221661509477\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Superfluous J\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 hours ago, Superfluous J said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA couple suggestions:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EA special kind of talent\u003C/strong\u003E - Destroy 2 or more \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E buildings in a single crash.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDid you check the map?\u003C/strong\u003E - Leave Kerbin\u0027s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E without having entered Mun\u0027s or Minmus\u0027 SOIs\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s some ideas to add onto yours;\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#ffffff;\u0022\u003E.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#ffffff;\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003EAchievements involving landing a spacecraft within 7 minutes of entering the atmosphere:\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESeven Minutes of Discomfort\u003C/strong\u003E - Land on Duna within 7 minutes of entering the atmosphere.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESeven Minutes of Fear\u003C/strong\u003E - Land on Eve with 7 minutes of entering the atmosphere.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESeven Minutes of Terror\u003C/strong\u003E - Land on Ovin within 7 minutes of entering the atmosphere.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAchievements involving putting heavy payloads into \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E:\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EHercules\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0- Put a\u00A0\u002B100t payload\u00A0into \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E in one launch.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003EAres\u00A0\u003C/b\u003E- Put a \u002B500t payload into \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E in one launch.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EZeus\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0- Put a \u002B1000t payload into \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E in one launch.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSome \u0027grand tour\u0027 fly-by achievements based on limited \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EDV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EHitchhiker\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0- Use a spacecraft with less than 1000 m/s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EDV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E to fly by all of Kerbol\u0027s planets and moons.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003EExplorer\u003C/b\u003E - Use a spacecraft with less than 500 m/s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EDV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E to fly by all of Kerbol\u0027s planets and moons.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVoyager\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0- Use a spacecraft with less than 250\u00A0m/s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EDV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E to fly by all of Kerbol\u0027s planets and moons.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf anything here seems a bit extreme or not hard enough, then updates to KSP 2 would bring in harder achievements so players push the limits of the game as hard as possible. Of course, they\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Ecould\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0use cheats, but hopefully the achievements have a check against that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-08-27T02:13:10Z\u0022 title=\u002208/27/2022 02:13  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 27, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by intelliCom\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just a random person","CreatedById":205722,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-26T16:31:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224167435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209512\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221661482425\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222633\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022hooray\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, hooray said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsome\u00A0points shop things\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat exactly do you mean by this?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224167515\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209512\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221661523294\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022209738\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022intelliCom\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, intelliCom said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOf course, they\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Ecould\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0use cheats, but hopefully the achievements have a check against that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI believe that\u0027s exactly how the console version of KSP 1 works.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BekfastDerp13","CreatedById":214450,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-26T17:40:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224167515\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209512\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221661523294\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022209738\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022intelliCom\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, intelliCom said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s some ideas to add onto yours;\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#ffffff;\u0022\u003E.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#ffffff;\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003EAchievements involving landing a spacecraft within 7 minutes of entering the atmosphere:\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESeven Minutes of Discomfort\u003C/strong\u003E - Land on Duna within 7 minutes of entering the atmosphere.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESeven Minutes of Fear\u003C/strong\u003E - Land on Eve with 7 minutes of entering the atmosphere.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESeven Minutes of Terror\u003C/strong\u003E - Land on Ovin within 7 minutes of entering the atmosphere.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAchievements involving putting heavy payloads into \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E:\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EHercules\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0- Put a\u00A0\u002B100t payload\u00A0into \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E in one launch.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003EAres\u00A0\u003C/b\u003E- Put a \u002B500t payload into \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E in one launch.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EZeus\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0- Put a \u002B1000t payload into \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E in one launch.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSome \u0027grand tour\u0027 fly-by achievements based on limited \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EDV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EHitchhiker\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0- Use a spacecraft with less than 1000 m/s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EDV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E to fly by all of Kerbol\u0027s planets and moons.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003EExplorer\u003C/b\u003E - Use a spacecraft with less than 500 m/s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EDV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E to fly by all of Kerbol\u0027s planets and moons.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVoyager\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0- Use a spacecraft with less than 250\u00A0m/s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EDV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E to fly by all of Kerbol\u0027s planets and moons.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf anything here seems a bit extreme or not hard enough, then updates to KSP 2 would bring in harder achievements so players push the limits of the game as hard as possible. Of course, they\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Ecould\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0use cheats, but hopefully the achievements have a check against that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s one from me -\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EBattle of the Heroes\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003E(or Battle of the Kerbals): Land on Rask and Rusk with the same vessel.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-26T18:09:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224167481\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209512\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221661509477\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Superfluous J\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Superfluous J said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDid you check the map?\u003C/strong\u003E - Leave Kerbin\u0027s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E without having entered Mun\u0027s or Minmus\u0027 SOIs\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoing that is usually\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eeasier\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0than entering one of the moons\u0027 SOIs. I\u0027d say this achievement would involve entering a solar orbit, spending \u0026gt;100 days out then re-entering Kerbin\u0027s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E without having visited another \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E along the way, with\u00A0the achievement title implying some kind of map-reading ineptitude as the navigator sends the craft in circles.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Look, there\u0027s Kerbin again. Auto, are you sure you...\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022It\u0027s a shortcut, Trust me\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"joratto","CreatedById":218497,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-29T14:21:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224167515\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209512\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221661523294\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022209738\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022intelliCom\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/26/2022 at 3:14 PM, intelliCom said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s some ideas to add onto yours;\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#ffffff;\u0022\u003E.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#ffffff;\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003EAchievements involving landing a spacecraft within 7 minutes of entering the atmosphere:\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESeven Minutes of Discomfort\u003C/strong\u003E - Land on Duna within 7 minutes of entering the atmosphere.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESeven Minutes of Fear\u003C/strong\u003E - Land on Eve with 7 minutes of entering the atmosphere.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESeven Minutes of Terror\u003C/strong\u003E - Land on Ovin within 7 minutes of entering the atmosphere.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAchievements involving putting heavy payloads into \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E:\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EHercules\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0- Put a\u00A0\u002B100t payload\u00A0into \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E in one launch.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003EAres\u00A0\u003C/b\u003E- Put a \u002B500t payload into \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E in one launch.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EZeus\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0- Put a \u002B1000t payload into \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E in one launch.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSome \u0027grand tour\u0027 fly-by achievements based on limited \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EDV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EHitchhiker\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0- Use a spacecraft with less than 1000 m/s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EDV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E to fly by all of Kerbol\u0027s planets and moons.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003EExplorer\u003C/b\u003E - Use a spacecraft with less than 500 m/s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EDV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E to fly by all of Kerbol\u0027s planets and moons.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVoyager\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0- Use a spacecraft with less than 250\u00A0m/s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EDV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E to fly by all of Kerbol\u0027s planets and moons.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf anything here seems a bit extreme or not hard enough, then updates to KSP 2 would bring in harder achievements so players push the limits of the game as hard as possible. Of course, they\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Ecould\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0use cheats, but hopefully the achievements have a check against that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope they wouldn\u0027t completely disable achievements on a save just for using cheats. If ksp2 is anywhere near as buggy as ksp1, then occasional cheating will be essential to prevent frustrating glitches from ruining hours of gameplay.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"shdwlrd","CreatedById":113880,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-29T14:56:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224168590\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209512\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221661782916\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022218497\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022joratto\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n29 minutes ago, joratto said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope they wouldn\u0027t completely disable achievements on a save just for using cheats. If ksp2 is anywhere near as buggy as ksp1, then occasional cheating will be essential to prevent frustrating glitches from ruining hours of gameplay.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBuggy or not, most games will disable achievements (for that save) if cheats or mods are used. Most devs only give achievements to players that only play the stock version, with stock rules and assets.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"joratto","CreatedById":218497,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-29T15:00:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224168604\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209512\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221661784999\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022113880\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022shdwlrd\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, shdwlrd said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBuggy or not, most games will disable achievements (for that save) if cheats or mods are used. Most devs only give achievements to players that only play the stock version, with stock rules and assets.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmost mainstream games aren\u0027t as buggy and grindy as ksp\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just a random person","CreatedById":205722,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-29T15:35:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224168606\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209512\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221661785254\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022218497\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022joratto\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n35 minutes ago, joratto said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmost mainstream games aren\u0027t as buggy and grindy as ksp\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLet\u0027s hope ksp2 won\u0027t either\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-29T16:27:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224168606\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209512\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221661785254\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022218497\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022joratto\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, joratto said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmost mainstream games aren\u0027t as buggy and grindy as ksp\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf KSP2 is like that too it will have failed at the only thing it was supposed to do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"joratto","CreatedById":218497,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-29T17:19:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224168636\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209512\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221661790429\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002268648\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Master39\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n52 minutes ago, Master39 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf KSP2 is like that too it will have failed at the only thing it was supposed to do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019ll believe it when I see it. I, for one, would realistically consider it a success even if it\u2019s just a parts/planets pack with better graphics and multiplayer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}